---
title: Greek Roasted Cauliflower and Bulgur Pilaf with Tzatziki
description: Roasting cauliflower transforms it into a hearty main dish! Our Greek cauliflower is served on a bed of whole-grain bulgur, making this dish both healthy and filling. Tzatziki - everyone's favourite Greek condiment - is a tangy, flavour-packed topping to finish it off.
